sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Agent
    participant AGW as Agentgateway Proxy
    participant Backend as Backend (LLM / MCP / Agent)

    Client->>AGW: Request (no credentials)
    AGW->>AGW: Basic auth check:<br/>No Authorization header
    AGW-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    Client->>AGW: Request + Authorization: Basic base64(user:password)
    AGW->>AGW: Decode base64 credentials
    AGW->>AGW: Lookup user in policy config<br/>Verify APR1 hash (salt + password)

    alt Credentials valid
        AGW->>Backend: Forward request
        Backend-->>AGW: Response
        AGW-->>Client: 200 OK
    else Credentials invalid
        AGW-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over AGW,Backend: Configured via EnterpriseAgentgatewayPolicy:<br/>traffic.basicAuthentication<br/>Mode: Strict (require) or Optional (allow through)
